meta {
  title = Framework,
  description = A documentation framework powered by SvelteKit and the Tiramisu markup language.,
  order = 0,
  icon = layers
}

Tiramisu Docs is a documentation framework built on link { url = https://svelte.dev, SvelteKit } and the link { url = /docs/language, Tiramisu markup language }. Write your docs in code { .tiramisu } files — the framework handles routing, navigation, search, and everything else.

callout {
  type = warning,
  bold { Beta } — Tiramisu Docs is under active development. APIs and features may change. If you run into issues or want to contribute\, visit the link {
    url = https://github.com/pouya-eghbali/tiramisu-docs,
    GitHub repository
  }.
}

h2 { Quick Look }

Create a file, get a page:

codeblock {
  language = tiramisu,
  """
meta { title = Getting Started, order = 1, icon = rocket }

Welcome to my docs! Here's how to install:

codeblock { language = bash, "npm install my-library" }

And here's a basic example:

codeblock { language = typescript, "import { create } from 'my-library'
const instance = create({ debug: true })" }
"""
}

That's it. No config files, no routing setup, no build scripts. Drop a code { .tiramisu } file in code { src/docs/ } and it becomes a page.

h2 { Features }

cards {
  card {
    title = File-Based Routing,
    description = Pages are created from your file structure. Folders become sidebar groups automatically.,
    icon = folder-tree
  },
  card {
    title = Built-In Search,
    description = Full-text search across all your documentation with zero configuration.,
    icon = search
  },
  card {
    title = Syntax Highlighting,
    description = Powered by Shiki with support for dozens of languages and dual themes.,
    icon = paintbrush
  },
  card {
    title = Dark Mode,
    description = Automatic light and dark theme switching out of the box.,
    icon = moon
  },
  card {
    title = Sections & i18n,
    description = Split docs into independent sections. Add translations with a folder per locale.,
    icon = globe
  },
  card {
    title = AI-Ready,
    description = Built-in MCP server and llms.txt generation for AI assistants.,
    icon = bot
  }
}

